name: Custom Car Design
description: Custom Vehicle Vinyl Design. Prices for decals are quoted based on design. You Provide your car make and model, color and a description of what you are looking for. You will receive an email that will let you know when do expect your design. (Within two weeks of order) You will receive the proof, two revisions included.

name: The Colorful Truth
description: Written By C.C. Warner Illustrated by Claire Warner This colorful tale shows children that there is an answer to today's pollution. Please preview, share, post, or just talk about it with your friends!!! The Colorful Truth is a magical tale about a little girl unhappy with her environment. No matter what she does, she is still, very unhappy. As the story goes, her wishes come true! "How," you say? You will have to get your hands on the copy by purchase or download! Please feel free to re-post! The Kiddos can use all the sunshine they get!
